            "name": "Tactics",
            "type": "section",
            "html": "<b>During Combat</b> The kobold uses her mutagen and extracts to strengthen her defense, and throws bombs at her enemies."
        },
        {
            "name": "Ecology",
            "type": "section",
            "html": "<b>Environment</b> temperate underground or deep forest"
